            <h6 class="mb-3 color-dark font-weight-bold"><i class="far fa-paper-plane color-dark font-weight-bold pe-2"></i>What is Mile(s) Apart?</h6>
            <p>
             sRide is a trusted social carpooling app that helps people to carpool by connecting people like you going your way. It uses a real-time matching process to help match people going in the same direction. Some of these users will be car owners (can give ride to other people to share cost) and some of these user will need ride.
            </p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 color-dark font-weight-bold"><i class="fas fa-pen-alt color-dark font-weight-bold pe-2"></i> What is carpooling?</h6>
            <p>
                Carpooling is when two or more people share a ride together. It allows individuals to reduce the costs and alleviate associated problems of congestion and emissions.
            </p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 color-dark font-weight-bold"><i class="fas fa-user color-dark font-weight-bold pe-2"></i>When can I use Mile(s) Apart to carpool?
            </h6>
            <p>
              <ul>
                <li>Commuting to work.</li>
                <li>Travel to different places on weekends.</li>
                <li>Get to movies,shopping,events and conferences with friends.</li>
              </ul>
            </p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 color-dark font-weight-bold"><i class="fas fa-rocket color-dark font-weight-bold ; pe-2"></i>What are the benifits of carpooling?
            </h6>
            <p>
             <ul>
                <li>Reduces Traffice</li>
                <li>Reduces carbon dioxide emmission thus reducing pollution.</li>
                <li>Reduces Parking Issues.</li>
                <li>Reduces burden of public Transportation.</li>
             </ul>
          </div>
      
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 color-dark font-weight-bold"><i class="fas fa-home color-dark font-weight-bold pe-2"></i> Do i need a car to carpool with Mile(s) Apart?
            
            </h6>
            <p> No,many people are happy to offer rides in exchange of sharing costs of the ride.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <h6 class="mb-3 color-dark font-weight-bold"><i class="fas fa-book-open color-dark font-weight-bold pe-2"></i> Can I use the same account to act as a Car owner and as a rider?</h6>
